nodes.text: Crate-busters were manual labor workers who worked loading and unloading cargo on starships. Some crate-busters were permanent members of a starship's crew, handling the transfer of cargo, or were employed by spaceports to conduct the same jobs. Crate-busters were usually from species that were physically powerful, such as the Sludir. Crate-busters used crate hooks to assist in their duties.
